snippet.title: Amber Heard Analysis: Interviews and Psychological Documentary Bio
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Psychological Analysis: Documentary / Biography 
In this video about Amber Heard, I analyze interesting moments from past interviews and make some new and (hopefully) original psychological observations to entertain you. I also discuss her relationships with Johnny Depp and others as well as the court case pending with Johnny Depp. 

Part 2 of my Amber Heard analysis: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6gUTTOGE7M&t=1772s
